!.vscode/extensions.json

# ─── kami skill: commit logic only ──────────────────────
# 폰트(51M)·예시 갤러리(showcase/demos/illustrations)는 무거워 로컬 전용.
# kami는 @font-face의 jsDelivr fallback + scripts/ensure-fonts.sh로 폰트 재provision.
.claude/skills/kami/assets/fonts/
.claude/skills/kami/assets/showcase/
.claude/skills/kami/assets/demos/
.claude/skills/kami/assets/illustrations/
